<section id="fs-id1960067" class="learning-objectives">
  <title>Learning Objectives</title>
<para id="fs-id1452194">By the end of this section, you will be able to:</para>
<list id="fs-id1776716">
<item>Define nuclear fusion.</item>
<item>Discuss processes to achieve practical fusion energy generation.</item>
</list>
<para id="fs-id1496665">The information presented in this section supports the following AP® learning objectives and science practices:</para><list id="fs-id1439948">
